<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1357947-please-could-somebody-write-the-final">Please, could somebody write the final lines of the book in Polish? I mean this one: I knew nothing, and I persisted in the faith that the time of cruel miracles was not past.</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
