<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">A literal translation (mine) is:<br/>“I knew nothing, persisting in unshaken faith that the time of cruel miracles was not passed.”<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">A literal translation (mine) is:<br />“I knew nothing, persisting in unshaken faith that the time of cruel miracles was not passed.”<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
