          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9780571219728" href="/book/show/251626.Solaris">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/4193760-hildur?shelf=read-on-kindle">read-on-kindle</a>, 
